snippet.title: Growing Up - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
An upcoming life sim by Vile Monarch. Your life is in your hands! Sculpt your childhood as well as parenthood with endless choices. Take control of what you learn, who you befriend, and find that special someone in this coming-of-age game.

Coming out in 2021! Add to wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1191120/Growing_Up/

Trailer song by Mikromusic.
